{"tid":612833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方放蛇拘19 PTGF 包括1印傭","createTime":"2018-04-01T07:15:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T11:49:29.000Z","uid":173591,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"19adec771479cc2bf47cab316b05904e42ffebb0","tid":612833,"uid":173591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T07:15:03.000Z","msg":"警方打擊<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>青少年援交</strong></span>拘捕19人。警方根據線報及經深入調查後，查悉有人利用網站及社交平台招攬青少年作「出租男友」或「出租女友」，實則進行援交賣淫，旺角警區特職隊於是採取「山河」行動，拘捕13男6女，當中一人為主腦，另外18人均為招攬目標，部分人為學生，當中最細的僅16歲，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">更有一名印尼女傭。</span>據了解，他們每做一宗「生意」，可獲1,000至4,000港元不等，主腦則從中抽佣。 <br />\n<br />\n消息稱，因為現時正值復活節假期，故警方加強打擊青少年罪行。警方將於稍後交代案情。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180401/mobile/bkn-20180401144554343-0401_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180401%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180401144554343-0401_00822_001.html&d=fO3Bk6jWbY6ghxLG0aYYBAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=01d53e07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180401/mobile/bkn-20180401144554343-0401_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n邊個咁撚重口味幫襯印印？"},{"pid":"ff554d09a56bf42face214cdfd796b0497cbfea0","tid":612833,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T07:16:28.000Z","msg":"今次好波呀！"},{"pid":"e0eef0b5893218e8cd9aae367db202b91bea0f5c","tid":612833,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T07:17:44.000Z","msg":"ig agent雞唔見少左"},{"pid":"037a80f942e4ea61484ee5e78c8478ca58d3f992","tid":612833,"uid":179962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T07:29:46.000Z","msg":"賓妹都出黎碌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8444999d8e483e8cbdd9e341d32d880115b4cd76","tid":612833,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T07:31:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.